caption.p: Geographic distribution of HIV-1 genotypes in recent infections in Yunnan. The dot density map for subtype B, subtype C, CRF01_AE, CRF07_BC, CRF08_BC, CRF55_01B, CRF55_01B, CRF64_BC, CRF83_cpx, CRF85_BC, CRF87_cpx and URFs shows the percentage of each genotype in each county. One dot was defined as 0.025% of the population
